# DOMAIN.md - [Project Name] Domain Model

Machine-readable domain model for AI-assisted development. Reference this document when working with project entities, APIs, or data.

## Core Entities

### [Entity Name]
Brief description of the entity's purpose.

| Field | Type | Constraints |
|-------|------|-------------|
| id | integer | Auto-increment primary key |
| name | string | Required, unique |
| status | enum | `active`, `archived` |
| created_at | string | ISO 8601 timestamp |

**Invariants:**
- `status` MUST be one of the allowed values
- `name` MUST be unique across all records
- Deleting an entity with active references MUST fail

### [Another Entity]
