## API Contract Rules

### Authentication
- All endpoints require `Authorization` header
- Invalid/missing credentials return `401 Unauthorized`

### Pagination
- Parameters: `page` (1-based, default 1), `limit` (default 20, max 100)
- Response includes pagination metadata

### Response Format
```
Success: { data: T[], pagination: { page, limit, total, totalPages } }
Single:  { data: T }
Error:   { error: string, status: number }
```

## Data Standards

| Standard | Rule |
|----------|------|
| Timestamps | ISO 8601 format |
| IDs | Auto-increment integers |
| Text encoding | UTF-8 |
| Naming | snake_case for fields, kebab-case for URLs |
